==Notes==

* A Draft Wire can be edited with the [[Draft_Edit|Draft Edit]] command.
* A Draft Wire can be converted to a [[Draft_BSpline|Draft BSpline]] with the [[Draft_WireToBSpline|Draft WireToBSpline]] command.
